title: INSIGHT: UAE launches the world's longest zipline
text:
INSIGHT: UAE launches the world's longest zipline 4:46pm GMT - 00:36 
The world's longest zipline opens in the United Arab Emirates, propelling thrill-seekers at speeds of up to 150 kilometers an hour down the Middle East country's highest mountain peak. ▲ Hide Transcript ▶ View Transcript
